that the sugar thing sneaks in.

00:33:22.520 --> 00:33:24.670
So if it's like a
fucking-- sorry.

00:33:24.670 --> 00:33:26.480
I love gummies.

00:33:26.480 --> 00:33:30.050
And I love almond milk ice
cream and stuff like that.

00:33:30.050 --> 00:33:31.400
MELISSA HARTWIG: Sure, yeah.

00:33:31.400 --> 00:33:34.900
AUDIENCE: But I noticed that
actually, interestingly enough,

