00:33:47.500 --> 00:33:49.480
and if it is the sugar.

00:33:49.480 --> 00:33:50.730
I mean, that would make sense.

00:33:50.730 --> 00:33:53.280
But I've heard also
before, perhaps,

00:33:53.280 --> 00:33:59.716
that your body level sets and
